  "2026-04-01T12:00:15.766Z",cursor-agent,Task corresponds to plan workstream D.
  "2026-04-01T12:06:56.221Z",cursor-agent,"Expanded terminal compatibility regressions: tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts now asserts timeout diagnostic messaging and adds a deterministic maxBuffer overflow case; tests/unit/beads-command.spec.ts covers interactive TTY fail-fast for --file -. Validation evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/parse-utils.spec.ts tests/unit/beads-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (97/97)."
  "2026-04-01T18:53:11.621Z",cursor-agent,Task reopened to add regression coverage for long-run visibility and stubborn timeout handling so terminal/agent environments do not misinterpret active test runs as hangs.
  "2026-04-01T19:10:49.575Z",cursor-agent,"Expanded regressions: tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts now covers stubborn timeout termination and interactive heartbeat emission; tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts now covers deterministic completion when linked commands ignore SIGTERM. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts (90/90)."
